* **`distributeBoxesHelper` Recursive Function:**  This is the core of the solution. It efficiently calculates the "excess" or "deficit" of boxes at each node.  A positive value means a node has more than one box and can give some away. A negative value means a node needs more boxes. The absolute value of the excess/deficit is the number of moves needed at that node.
