     * Overall Space Complexity: O(N) or O(K), depending on distribution and whether N >> K, where N is the number of strings in the input list, and K is the number of distinct starting characters.

     * Thread Safety:  The ConcurrentHashMap and CopyOnWriteArrayList ensure thread safety when grouping the strings.  Synchronization is not required within the loop because the map operations are thread-safe.
