        // Test Case 4: Input Validation
        // Enter invalid shot options and confirm that the game prompts the user for
        // valid input.

        // Test Case 5: Play again
        // Test the 'play again' functionality by entering "yes" and then "no".

        //Edge Case: All wickets fall on 0 runs.
        //Edge Case: High score for one player.

        //Note:  These test cases are manual, but we can add automated testing to further enhance robustness.

    }
}
```

